1. Create it.
Create one or more items on the floor of this area. You can use Precious to copy an item if needed.

2. Customise it. 
You can change stats, vfxt, appearance, whatever you like.

3. Save it.
Click on one of the slot PLCs to safe the item(s) in the corresponding DMS item slot. You can see what you have saved in your DMS settings page in Admin Tools.
